{"lemma":"فَذُّ","slug":"فَذُّ","root":"ف.ذ.ذ","root_slug":"ف-ذ-ذ","root_link":"/words/roots/ف-ذ-ذ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n33297"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%81%D9%8E%D8%B0%D9%8F%D9%91"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be alone, to be isolated"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"alone, single, isolated"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"unique"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n33297","headword_ar":"فَذٌّ","root":"f*","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Single; sole; only; one, and no more;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and alone,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apart from others;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see 1;)] syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farodN","text_ar":"فَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Mgh, O, L, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAHidN","text_ar":"وَاحِدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L, Msb:) pl. [of mult.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fu*uw*N","text_ar":"فُذُوذٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, Msb, K) and [of pauc.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afo*aA*FA","text_ar":"اَفْذَاذًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, L, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ahabaA fa*~ayoni","text_ar":"ذَهَبَا فَذَّيْنِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They two went away singly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, L.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA=' Alqawoma","text_ar":"جَا=ء القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^afo*aA*FA","text_ar":"اَفْذَاذًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fu*aA*aY","text_ar":"فُذَاذَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamorN fa*~N","text_ar":"تَمْرٌ فَذٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dates that are separate, each one from others;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, M, O, L, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not sticking together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, M, L;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faD~N","text_ar":"فَضٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fav~N","text_ar":"فَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fv","text_ar":"فث"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfa*~u","text_ar":"الفَذُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [a name of]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The first of the arrows used in the game called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almayosir","text_ar":"المَيْسِر"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, M, O, L, K:) it has one notch; and for it is gained one share [of the slaughtered camel] when it is successful, and one share is exacted when it is unsuccessful: (Lh, M, O, L:) the arrows are ten: the 2nd is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~awoA^amu","text_ar":"التَّوْاَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the 3rd,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aqiybu","text_ar":"الرَّقِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the 4th,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHilosu","text_ar":"الحِلْسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the 5th,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAfisu","text_ar":"النَّافِسُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the 6th,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almusobilu","text_ar":"المُسْبِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the 7th,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuEal~aY","text_ar":"المُعَلَّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and there are three for which there is no share, namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~afiyHu","text_ar":"السَّفِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaniyHu","text_ar":"المَنِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwagodu","text_ar":"الوَغْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O, L.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alrqyb","text_ar":"الرقيب"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kalimapo fa*~apN","text_ar":"كَلِمَةْ فَذَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faA*~apN","text_ar":"فَاذَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["L","Msb","M","K","S","O","Lh"]}]}}